commit.message:
Update the learning rate schedule
Learning rate schedule has been update according to the empricial results.

Update the rotation angle in the augmentation
Rotation angle in the augmentation has been updated to -30 to 30 from -10 to 10.

Update the learning rate
The learning rate has been updated according the results of hyperparameter tuning.

Fix the sampling ratio issue in the dataloader
Bug in the dataloader for the sampling ratio has been fixed.

Set network to train mode after the eval mode is complete
Now the network is always set to eval model at the beginning and train mode at the end with in the test logic itself.
